## 7. CONFIGURAÇÃO E PARÂMETROS

### 7.1 Variáveis de Ambiente

```env
# Apify
APIFY_API_TOKEN=apify_api_xxx
APIFY_LINKEDIN_ACTOR_ID=apify/linkedin-scraper

# LLM
LLM_MODEL=claude-3-sonnet-20240229
LLM_TEMPERATURE=0.3
LLM_MAX_TOKENS=4096

# Storage
AUDIT_STORAGE_BUCKET=s3://lia-audits
RAW_DATA_RETENTION_DAYS=90
AUDIT_RETENTION_YEARS=2
```

### 7.2 Thresholds Configuráveis

```json
{
  "fusion": {
    "core_threshold": 0.6,
    "variant_threshold": 0.4,
    "min_confidence": 0.5
  },
  "analysis": {
    "min_skills_for_search": 3,
    "max_skills_in_query": 10,
    "min_titles_for_search": 1,
    "max_titles_in_query": 5
  },
  "quality": {
    "min_overall_confidence": 0.6,
    "require_human_review_below": 0.5
  }
}
```

